&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>zsh</title><link>https://kingye.me/note-cs/docs/tool/linux/centos/zsh/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://kingye.me/note-cs/docs/tool/linux/centos/zsh/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="zsh">
 zsh
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#zsh">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="oh-my-zshhttpsohmyzsh">
 &lt;a href="https://ohmyz.sh/">oh-my-zsh&lt;/a>
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#oh-my-zshhttpsohmyzsh">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>安装&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo yum install -y git zsh
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># sh -c &amp;#34;$(curl -fsSL https://raw.github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh)&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sh -c &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">$(&lt;/span>wget https://raw.github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh -O -&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">)&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>cat &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;lt;&amp;lt; &amp;#39;EOF&amp;#39; &amp;gt;&amp;gt; ~/.zshrc
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">export PROMPT=&amp;#39;%{$fg[magenta]%}%(?..%?%1v)%n@%{$fg[green]%}%M:%{$fg[cyan]%}%c%{$reset_color%} $(git_prompt_info)&amp;#39;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">EOF&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>zsh
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>alias cdcode&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;cd ~/code&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>alias cdstudy&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;cdcode &amp;amp;&amp;amp; cd study&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>alias cdtest&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;cdstudy &amp;amp;&amp;amp; cd test&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>alias cdgithub&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;cdcode &amp;amp;&amp;amp; cd github&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>alias cdgitlab&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;cdcode &amp;amp;&amp;amp; cd gitlab&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>alias cdbitbucket&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;cdcode &amp;amp;&amp;amp; cd bitbucket&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># proxy&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># export http_proxy=149.28.137.166:20171&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># export https_proxy=149.28.137.166:20171&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 设置默认为 zsh&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo chsh -s /usr/bin/zsh yewang
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>